            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <supplied reason="lost">In honorem</supplied> divinae domus et <expan><abbr>col</abbr><ex>oniae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Iul</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustae</ex></expan> Phil<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>ipp</abbr><ex>iensium</ex></expan></supplied> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost">ex</supplied> voluntate sua a divo <supplied reason="lost">A</supplied>ntonino ex epulis <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost"><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aio</ex></expan> Modio Laeto Rufiniano, <expan><abbr>q</abbr><ex>uaestore</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> p</supplied><expan><abbr>r</abbr><ex>aetore</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>provinc</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Maced</abbr><ex>oniae</ex></expan> cura<supplied reason="lost">tor</supplied>e <expan><abbr>r</abbr><ex>ei</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ublicae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Philipp</abbr><ex>iensium</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die Inschrift besteht aus vier zu dem Architrav des Tempels gehörenden Blöcken, derer Längen 152, 163, 200 und 237 cm betragen. (B): Abweichende Textgestaltung.</p>
            </div>
